snippet.title: Deep Inside — Gameplay Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2968020/Deep_Inside/

Deep Inside is a first-person psychological horror game! You are a police officer who has to find out who is behind the most high-profile murders in the city. Use your detective skills to catch the killer, but remember that the truth can be bitter!

#horrorgame #indiegame #gamedev
